data.description: Welcome to your beautifully maintained Two-bedroom, two bathroom. As you enter, you are greeted by an inviting foyer that leads to the heart of the home—an open-concept living space. The spacious living room is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quiet evenings with friends.   This community is located a few minutes from Super Walmart, a quick drive to The University of Florida and UF Health Shands and walking/ biking distance to local favorite spots such as: Tom Petty Park, Downtown Gainesville and Satchel's Pizza. Come see, you will not be disappointed.  Schedule a showing today, because this gem won't last long!  Buyer is responsible to verify all information contained within this listing All information on this page is considered reliable, but not guaranteed.
